Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/rezaiyan/claude-notifier
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: claude-notifier
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, libnotify-bin
Recommends: xdotool
Description: Desktop notifications for Claude Code
 Fires a desktop notification when Claude Code finishes a task or is
 waiting for your input, so you can switch away and come back when needed.
 Supports macOS and Linux. On Linux, notifications are sent via notify-send
 and focus detection uses xdotool (X11 only).
